title: Potential | Episode 6
description:
While Clementine just wants to avoid the world, Shadow is ready to take their powers to the next level. Crewdson tries to warn Dodson of what’s coming. Clementine discovers Veronica at Evan’s house and erupts in anger. We learn Clementine’s darkest secret. [Adult Content, Adult Language, Violence]
